{"tid":213335,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"點解多數ram都有永久保養?","createTime":"2017-04-23T05:23:34.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-24T04:32:01.000Z","uid":88374,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4404049a3e0102fbbf3966480722c6240a684dc7","tid":213335,"uid":88374,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T05:23:34.000Z","msg":"一部電腦有幾part零件如motherboard,display card,cpu,psu,etc.<br />\n每種零件都有佢特定既warranty period<br />\n例如motherboard,cpu,display card多數係3年,low-cost psu多數3年,high-cost psu多數5年<br />\n<br />\n但點解ram偏偏最正最特別?<br />\n有lifetime既保養期呢?<br />\n<br />\n你用兩三舊水買完一條ram就可以用成世咁正?<br />\n<br />\n間ram公司或者ram廠唔會蝕撚死咩?<br />\n<br />\n佢地點賺錢?<br />\n<br />\n點解其他零件唔提供永久保養?<br />\n<br />\n呢到有一個較片面既解釋<br />\n擇自 Quora:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.quora.com/Why-does-computer-RAM-have-a-lifetime-warranty\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.quora.com%2FWhy-does-computer-RAM-have-a-lifetime-warranty&d=LJfbHi1nzQR09hbgKwAG17ZGMQxn7aheim1dKZ3ASAU%3D&h=03d50dba\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.quora.com/Why-does-computer-RAM-have-a-lifetime-warranty</a><br />\n<br />\n可能你睇唔明英文<br />\n我會用另一種方法解釋俾你聽<br />\n<br />\n先回到最基本既問題<br />\n點解電子零件公司要推出保養政策?<br />\n就係為消費者提供免費維修既服務<br />\n即係將消費者買左零件之後既維修成本<br />\n轉嫁返俾自己<br />\n<br />\n係經濟學上<br />\n即係承擔返感知風險(Perceived Risk)中既財務風險<br />\n因產品有質量問題而招致經濟上蒙受損失所產生既風險<br />\n從而就減少左條友係購買時既考慮<br />\n咁就增加左成功出售既機會<br />\n(俾條link大家:<a href=\"https://www.thebalance.com/what-is-perceived-risk-2295541\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebalance.com%2Fwhat-is-perceived-risk-2295541&d=LJfbHi1nzQR09hbgKwAG17ZGMQxn7aheim1dKZ3ASAU%3D&h=cf630195\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thebalance.com/what-is-perceived-risk-2295541</a>)<br />\n<br />\n同埋另一個冇咁明顯同普遍既<br />\n就係硬件公司多數都係直接換舊新既俾你<br />\n幾分鐘就搞掂<br />\n你去幫襯D濕9電腦舖就可能要等幾個鐘<br />\n所以佢又幫你減少左時間風險<br />\n修理或退還造成的時間浪費而帶來的風險<br />\n<br />\n但係比較長遠既人就會諗<br />\n有限保養過左之後<br />\n堆風險咪都係自己一個承擔返<br />\n間公司只承擔左短期既風險<br />\n之後由你承擔返<br />\n<br />\n咁你就諗到<br />\n點解ram有lifetime既保養期<br />\n其中一個原因就係為左再減少個堆長遠撚既考慮而設既<br />\n<br />\n但另一個原因<br />\n心理因素<br />\n堆人見到Lifetime保養就會打晒飛機<br />\n可以用一世<br />\n咁又買啦<br />\n<br />\n講住咁多先<br />\n仲有好多野未講<br />\n唔打住"},{"pid":"9409e8918537a3530b503231b881a865f772d874","tid":213335,"uid":75139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T05:33:37.000Z","msg":"到你用新一代個陣條ram 都未壞 (adata 除外)"},{"pid":"e38daabc34bb97dce68070e33518fc269a0d64b5","tid":213335,"uid":88374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T05:34:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>到你用新一代個陣條ram 都未壞 (adata 除外)</blockquote><br />\n呢個係其中一個因素<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95e5bcad95cc86afc42523888f55447d1696045e","tid":213335,"uid":50196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T05:44:00.000Z","msg":"留名學野"},{"pid":"98de6c871aebda0221b12a938d31ba4276b90b56","tid":213335,"uid":51817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T05:48:52.000Z","msg":"用貴啲嘅ram 電腦會唔會run得快啲？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"697ed730fead47ebd1e1b124473a116eb486bca7","tid":213335,"uid":5178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T06:06:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>用貴啲嘅ram 電腦會唔會run得快啲？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n跑分實會"},{"pid":"c399e49b8cd0651ab5e14f4533367adc86b97c52","tid":213335,"uid":79829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T06:07:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>用貴啲嘅ram 電腦會唔會run得快啲？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n跑分實會</blockquote><br />\n打機都會"},{"pid":"35f018bb1b4aa41e1b447757580fb581c426edc3","tid":213335,"uid":60967,"like":